import React, { Component, Fragment } from 'react'
import { Form, FormGroup, Label, Button, Input, Row, Container, Col } from 'reactstrap';

class Connexion extends Component {
    render () {
        return (
            <Fragment>
                <Container>
                <Form>
                        <Row>
                            <Col>
                                <FormGroup>
                                    <Label for="firstname">Prénom</Label>
                                    <Input type="text" name="firstname" id="firstname" placeholder="Prénom" />
                                </FormGroup>
                            </Col>
                        
                        <FormGroup>
                            <Label for="lastname">Nom</Label>
                            <Input type="text" name="lastname" id="lastname" placeholder="Nom" />
                        </FormGroup>
                        </Row>
                        <FormGroup>
                            <Label for="email">Email</Label>
                            <Input type="email" name="email" id="email" placeholder="exemple@exemple.com" />
                        </FormGroup>
                        <FormGroup>
                            <Label for="password">Mot de passe</Label>
                            <Input type="password" name="password" id="password" placeholder="Mot de passe " />
                        </FormGroup>
                        <FormGroup>
                            <Label for="corfirmPassword">Mot de passe</Label>
                            <Input type="password" name="corfirmPassword" id="corfirmPassword" placeholder="Corfirmation du mot de passe" />
                        </FormGroup>
                        <Button type="submit">S'inscrire</Button>
                    </Form>
                </Container>
            </Fragment>
        )
    }
}

export default Connexion
